General.Name: Methanex Corporation
General.Description: Methanex Corporation produces and supplies methanol in Asia Pacific, North America, Europe, and South America. It owns and leases storage and terminal facilities. The company serves chemical and petrochemical producers. Methanex Corporation was incorporated in 1968 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
